Name: Summer Framed Suncatcher Painting Kit
Description: Decorate your very own suncatcher painting and place your art creation in a windowsill to see the bright colors! Ages 6 & up.

Name: Acrylic Paint Value Pack
Description: This versatile acrylic paint set includes a range of classic colors, perfect for general arts and crafts, stenciling, ceramics, school projects, home decorating and decorative painting. The colors in this set include: purple, bright blue, brown, golden brown, dark gray, black, white, bright red, orange, bright yellow, grass green, and turquoise.

Name: Washable Sidewalk Chalk, 48ct.
Description: Whether you want to surprise your kids with a fun springtime activity or need to fill space during a rainy afternoon, this paint your own kit from Creatology has got you covered. Pair this with our other sets for fun the entire family can enjoy or for a night of DIY activities!

Name: CharismaÂ® Tweed Stripe Yarn
Description: Indulge your creativity with this tweed-style skein. Make a knit coat or cardigan inspired by the classic tweed blazer or a comfy blanket, scarf or hat! The Tweed Stripe is a wonderfully soft, bulky weight yarn that works up into classically colored stripes with a touch of tweed.

Name: 36 Color Watercolor Pan Set
Description: The full spectrum of brilliant colors in this watercolor palette make it a great gift for a beginner painter interested in experimenting with watercolor paints. All of the watercolor pans in the set are water soluble. This set includes 36 colors and a natural hair brush to help you get started.

Name: 10 Pack 8" x 10" Super Value Canvas
Description: Perfect for students or working artists, this canvas set provides great quality at a great value. Each cotton duck canvas is acrylic titanium triple primed with acid-free sizing. Ideal for acrylic or oil painting, each canvas is stretched and back stapled to a 5/8" kiln dried wooden frame.

Name: Construction Paper, 96ct.
Description: Crayola 96 Count Construction Paper is a must-have for home and school projects. This pack includes 96 sheets of Construction Paper in standard 9" x 12" paper size. There are 8 different colors including: Pink, Red, Orange, Yellow, Green, Blue, Violet, and Black.
